description: For sale: $420,000. Secluded 2+bedroom year round log cabin with spectacular unspoiled views of Niles Bay. Open design with vaulted log ceilings, reclaimed hardwood flooring, glass doors onto lakeside sunroom with access to outdoor decks. Lower level includes two spacious bedrooms, bath with walk in shower, utility room with washer/dryer, and large walk out entrance to lakeside path.  Newer propane furnace, storage building, lift out dock, and snowmobile trail to the lake all included.  The warmth of the logs, custom light fixture, and northwoods decor creates the true cabin life.  An incredible package!

For sale: $479,000. Explore Lake Vermilion from this welcoming 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath home located on a private drive.

This 1.9 acre double lake lot offers mature pines, sandy beach, 311 feet of shoreline and beautiful sunsets over Spring Bay.

The 2-story, 2000 sq. ft. home has been recently updated and comes with new carpet, all new appliances, remodeled baths, gas fireplace, hardwood floors and cedar siding.

The property also features an insulated garage with finished upstairs office and storage space, stone fire pit with lake view, and 40' dock.

A short walk to Moosebirds for ice cream or The Landing for dinner. Nearest public water access 0.3 mi away.

*** Please call 218-251-3728 or email sellwill@gmail.com for more information or to schedule a showing.

description: For sale: $1,750,000. One Of A Kind Very Rare Waterfront Property On One Of Nat Geo's Top 10 Most Scenic Lakes In The USA, Lake Vermilion.
